summary: Adds a new greatsword to the game.
descriptionHtml:
Was planning on releasing this later as a custom quest reward, you know, once CK comes out and i know how to make quests.
At the minute it\'s just a standalone greatsword.
Found under daedra category.
Thought i\'d put it out there to see the response.

Extract to data folder.
